<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Fragment from the upper part of a <rs type="material">marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> lid, with one of the projections  (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.27</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.17</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.15</measure>); projection complete, but lid broken both to left and right.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in two hands, a. on projection; b. along upper edge..</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>a. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.06-0.07</measure>; small <foreign lang="grc">Ι</foreign> inside <foreign lang="grc">Σ</foreign>; the possibility that this is an elaborate serif should perhaps be noted. b. uneven and poorly cut letters; square <term lang="grc-Latn">sigma</term>; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02-0.025</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>a. <date notBefore="-0100" notAfter="-0001" exact="none" cert="low">First century B.C.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>); b. probably <date notBefore="0201" notAfter="0300" exact="none">third century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
