</div>

<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>a. not usefully translatable.</p><p>b. <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character" dim="left"/> <supplied reason="lost">the</supplied> place <supplied reason="subaudible">belongs to   </supplied> <seg cert="low">M</seg><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character" dim="right"/></p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p> It would appear that a fairly early sarcophagus had been re-used at a comparatively late date. One would expect a. to give the owner(s)' names.</p>
</div>
